WEBVTT

00:12:27.495 --> 00:12:30.491
Tunaweza pia kutumia hii
katika utafiti wa masoko,

00:12:30.515 --> 00:12:32.366
kwa mfano, kujua

00:12:32.390 --> 00:12:36.745
kama watu wanapenda au hawapendi
bidhaa fulani za matumizi.

00:12:37.229 --> 00:12:39.467
Tunaweza hata kutumia kwenye miadi.

00:12:39.904 --> 00:12:41.064
Sasa kwa mfano

00:12:41.088 --> 00:12:43.682
Ikiwa mliyeahidiana anakuonyesha tabasamu,

00:12:43.706 --> 00:12:46.500
teknolojia hii inaweza kukusaidia kujua

00:12:46.524 --> 00:12:49.131
kama anakupenda kweli

00:12:49.155 --> 00:12:51.330
au anajaribu tu kuonyesha wema kwako.

00:12:51.864 --> 00:12:53.559
Na kwa suala hili,

00:12:53.583 --> 00:12:55.459
anajaribu kuonyesha wema kwako.

00:12:55.483 --> 00:12:57.875
(Kicheko)

00:12:59.244 --> 00:13:02.953
Hivyo teknolojia ya transdermal optical
imaging